WEBVTT

00:00:01.523 --> 00:00:04.714
What is up with us white people?

00:00:04.738 --> 00:00:06.364
(Laughter)

00:00:07.685 --> 00:00:10.284
I've been thinking about that a lot
the last few years,

00:00:10.308 --> 00:00:11.772
and I know I have company.

00:00:12.271 --> 00:00:13.579
Look, I get it --

00:00:13.603 --> 00:00:16.589
people of color have been asking
that question for centuries.

00:00:17.335 --> 00:00:21.664
But I think a growing number
of white folks are too,

00:00:21.688 --> 00:00:24.681
given what's been going on out there

00:00:24.705 --> 00:00:25.970
in our country.

00:00:27.537 --> 00:00:30.882
And notice I said,
"What's up with us white people?"